trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventArgs" /> that contains the event data.

Represents the method that will handle the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected" /> and <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected" /> events of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager" /> control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected" /> 컨트롤의 <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected" /> 및 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager" /> 이벤트를 처리할 메서드를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventHandler> class defines a handler delegate for two events that occur on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control: the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> event and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> event.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventHandler> 클래스 정의에서 발생 하는 두 개의 이벤트 처리기 대리자는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> 제어:는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> 이벤트 및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: The method that handles the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> event is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnected%2A> method.

The method that handles the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> event is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnected%2A> method.
In both cases, the event data are contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventArgs> object.
trans-unit.target: 두 경우 모두, 이벤트 데이터에 포함 되어는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventArgs> 개체입니다.
